title: Kritsana Klanklin
text:
Kritsana Klanklin (Thai: กฤษณะ กลั่นกลิ่น; born 26 February 1984) is a professional footballer from Thailand.  He is currently playing for Police Tero in Thai League 2.He played for Krung Thai Bank in the 2008 AFC Champions League group stages.


== Honours ==


=== Club ===
Bangkok GlassSingapore Cup Winner (1): 2010
